title: Transylbabies
description: A mission to babysit Snowmanpire babies in Transylbiria leads Vambre and Prohyas to attack the local monster townsfolk in misguided attempts to keep the Snowbabies safe.

title: Swing Set Jet Set
description: Axel and the team battle Princess SugarSalt for possession of Bearbarian's hammer, traded to her by one of their own - Galileo!

title: To Air Is Robot
description: Air Man stakes a claim on the skies above Silicon City, threatening anything that trespasses on his airspace.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Esforzarse Mas
description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se llevan a Mao Mao y a Colosal, depende de Adorabat salvarlos a ambos.

title: Schnorp
description: The Thunderkittens plug a new video game cartridge into Snarf only to learn that it didn't load a game, it loaded a whole new personality into their pal! Meet Schnorp, a kind Swedish man who loves the beauty of nature and collecting berries! Schnorp is loads of fun, but we're gonna want Snarf back, right?

title: The Explorer's Club
description: The ninja must break into the Explorer's Club to obtain the second Scroll of Forbidden Spinjitzu, running afoul of the club's manager and irate club-members.

title: Sister Sitter
description: When Blossom and Bubbles get sick, Buttercup volunteers to take care of them for the day.

title: Burrito
description: A Pardo le gustan los burritos. Mucho. Tanto que cuando un restaurant elabora un Burrito tamaño oso, Pardo se obliga a comer semejante obra de arte majestuosa. Lleva el burrito consigo a todas partes y lo convierte en una parte nueva y cada vez más olorosa de su vida.

title: Soy Dendy
description: K.O. ayuda a Dendy, una niña extraña de la escuela, a conseguir las piezas que necesita para reparar su mochila de alta tecnología.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: License to Drill
description: Mega Man teams up with Bert Wily to take down Drill Man, whose plan to construct hundreds of drill shaped high rises has put Silicon City in both aesthetic and physical danger!

title: Itch to Explore
description: Craig's quest to map the entire Creek takes him and his friends into the treacherous Poison Ivy Grove.

title: Chico Solitario
description: Cuando a Adorabat le cuesta conocer amigos nuevos en la escuela, Mao Mao le cuenta la historia de cómo conoció a su primer amigo real...Bao Bao.

title: Out to Launch
description: While on a visit to Cape Canaveral, the Tennyson Trio are present for the inaugural launch of an experimental space plane. When Vilgax commandeers the ship, Ben must stop the baddie from weaponizing the shuttle before the countdown hits zero.

title: Last One There
description: When Unikitty accidentally invokes an ancient curse, the gang must beat Master Frown and Brock back to the castle before one of them literally turns into a rotten egg.

title: Watt's Happening?!
description: When Elec Man derails the school play by hijacking Silicon Central's power, Aki/Mega Man must use what he has learned onstage to defeat his supercharged foe.

title: Alone Quest
description: Craig has an "emergency" leaving Kelsey alone at the Stump.

title: Robo Teacher
description: When a substitute teacher fills in for Chef, Duncan thinks it's going to be the best day ever. He's wrong.

title: While You Were Away
description: Dr. Psychobos and Princess Attea have invaded Rook's home planet Revonnah with an army of Incurseans! (Introducing new Ben alien, Astrodactyl.)

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: Cartoon Feud
description: Control Freak forces the Titans and the Scooby Gang to compete on Family Feud.

title: Lucky Ducky Mug
description: When Adorabat and Badgerclops break Mao Mao's favorite mug, he gives them the silent treatment.

title: Capullos de Rosa
description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

title: Don't Read the Comments
description: An obsession with comments and criticisms about him on the Board of Opinions drives Prohyas nuts, affecting Warrior missions for the worse and raising Vambre's ire, I mean, concerns.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Superstar Dan/Awesome Brawlers on Vacation
description: Superstar Dan: The Awesome Brawler's head to Tokyo for the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition. While Wynton, Shun, Lia and Lightning see the sites, and enjoy the tastes of Japan, Dan, as the Los Volmos Champion, has official Bakugan Battle League duties and obligations that keep him busy./Awesome Brawlers on Vacation: Lia, Lightning, Shun and Wynton explore the sights of Toyko when a rogue Bakugan shows up and rampages. The Awesome Brawlers have to spring into action, rolling out their Bakugan to stop the rogue enemy before any real damage can be done.

title: Chaqueta De Mezclilla
description: Los Osos encuentran una chaqueta de jean deslumbrante en un contenedor de basura. Es una de las cosas más fabulosas que jamás hayan visto, y parece convertir a aquel que la use en una persona extremadamente afortunada. Pero cuando los Osos discuten para ver quién queda a cargo de la chaqueta, empiezan a pensar que su bendición de denim se convirtió en una maldición.

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 1
description: As the Autobots on the Ark prepare to land on Cybertron, Chromia and Perceptor attempt to escape Decepticon captivity.

title: Cambiando Objetos
description: Axel y el equipo luchan contra la Princesa SugarSalt por la posesión del martillo de Bearbarian, que le vendió uno de los suyos: iGalileo!

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Tales from the Omnitrix
description: Team Tennyson trade campfire stories in an anthology-style series that pits Ben against his archrival, Kevin 11, and teaches our hero the power of imagination.

title: Pleito animado
description: Control Fenómeno obliga a los Titanes y a la Scooby-pandilla a competir en Pleito Familiar.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ninjas Shhh
description: Los Osos están hartos de la decadencia actual del protocolo en los cines. ¿Tú no lo estás? Tras autoproclamarse "la policía de los cines", se cuelan como ninjas para hacer callar a las personas que arruinan con sus malos modales la experiencia del ir al cine.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Battle for the Bottled City
description: Atom shrinks Superman so he can visit his fellow Kryptonians in the bottled city of Kandor. Soon after, Brainiac attacks and takes off with the bottle. Atom is forced to take control of one of Superman's damaged robots in order to follow after Brainiac and retrieve the city.

title: Rose Buds
description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

title: Buen Viaje
description: Abordo del SS Pettigrew en su último viaje, Ben debe luchar no solo contra el mareo sino también contra Vapor Smythe, que se propone usar a sus criaturas mecánicas para hundir el barco moderno que remplaza al vapor... iy a sus pasajeros!

title: For a Few Duncans More
description: While trying to photocopy his butt on Chef's fancy new copier Duncan accidentally makes an entire other Duncan. Great! This other Duncan can do all the school stuff while the real Duncan chills. But things go badly when the other Duncan decides to copy himself so he can chill too.

title: Osos Habitantes
description: Pardo, Panda y Polar no son más que tres forasteros en busca de un camino que los lleve a la adaptación... y si pueden conseguir algo de helado (o, en lo posible, yogur helado descremado) en el camino, imucho mejor! En cada episodio se muestran las desventuras cotidianas de los osos, que buscan comida, hacen todo tipo de tonterías y lidian unos con otros y con el mundo que los rodea. Sea cual sea la situación que enfrentan, está claro que ser un oso en un mundo civilizado y moderno no es tarea sencilla.

title: Dia de Elecciones
description: Manzana se presenta como candidato a alcalde.

title: Big Trouble for Tiny Miracle
description: Tiny Miracle allows the gang to take advantage of his generosity at the expense of his own health.

title: I Am Dendy
description: KO helps a strange girl from school, Dendy, get the parts she needs to repair her high tech backpack.

title: Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray
description: Dr. Animo has broken out of jail, and has been tracking down Ben, intent on revenge. At the same time, Ben's broken off a piece of the Omnitrix, and as a result, has turned into weird alien combinations, i.e. StinkArms.

title: Pintura dolorosa
description: Leshawna inventa una pelea con globos llenos de pintura para ver quién va al parque de diversiones con ella.

title: This Man, This Man Man!
description: When Guts Man goes on a ravenous rampage across the city, Mega Man must turn to an unlikely ally, Man Man, a bumbling DIY human analog to our hero.

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: Jamas Confies en un Humano
description: Mientras Aspheera busca vengarse del "Engañador Traicionero" que la traicionó, el ninja hace un sorprendente descubrimiento.

title: Mision solitaria
description: Craig debe atender una "emergencia", dejando a Kelsey sola en el Tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Burrito
description: Grizz likes Burritos. A lot. So much so that after a restaurant makes a Bear-Sized Burrito, Grizz can't bring himself to eat such a majestic work of art. He carries the burrito everywhere making it a new and increasingly smelly part of his life.

title: Porcupunk Rock
description: Madcap turns to Axel and his team for help after a sonic upgrade to Porcupunk threatens to bring down the house.

title: Pequena Escuela Madre
description: Bienvenidos a la Pequeña Escuela Madre, un lugar en la Tierra donde Gemas de todo el universo pueden aprender a vivir juntas pacíficamente. Pero hay una Gema que se rehúsa a asistir.

title: Continue?
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman hires the Warriors to retrieve the Orb of Sphericity from a temple in Galacton. The odd thing is, this temple has save points! When the Warriors are defeated, they respawn, but Vambre remembers what happened and Prohyas does not.

title: Sword Heist
description: When a local sword shop sells an ultra powerful sword to Ratar-O, Lion-O decides he has to steal it before Ratar-O can come pick it up. Unfortunately Lion-O is completely against stealing, but luckily he knows someone who loves to steal, Lion-S!

title: Despeguemos
description: De excursión en Cabo Cañaveral, el trío Tennyson presencia el lanzamiento inaugural de una nave espacial experimental, pero cuando Vilgax comanda la nave, Ben debe impedir que el villano use el transbordador como arma antes de que la cuenta regresiva llegue a cero.

title: Try Hard
description: When the Sky Pirates take Mao Mao and Badgerclops hostage, it's up to Adorabat to save the day.

title: La Venganza es Mia
description: Aspheera llega al Monasterio de Spinjitzu y se enfrenta a Wu, obligando a uno de los ninjas a hacer un sacrificio heroico.

title: Ganas de Explorar
description: La misión de Craig de mapear el Arroyo entero los lleva a él y a sus amigos a arboleda traicionera de Hiedra Venenosa
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: El Desnudo de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao pierde la ropa mientras intenta escalar el Rubí Puro Corazón, tiene que regresar al cuartel general antes de que amanezca.

title: Let's Be Friends
description: KO wants to become friends with Enid and Rad and get hired at Lakewood Plaza Turbo.

title: The Other Fight
description: Eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League, Ajit is airlifted by drone to a massive cargo ship in the middle of Tokyo Bay. Now that he's on board the cargo ship, he must rescue Dan and Drago, and stop whoever is sabotaging the Battle League. Dan and Ajit investigate the mysterious cargo ship that the eliminated brawlers and Bakugan are being held on. Dan races to track down Drago, but along the way runs into a familiar face.

title: Chill Out, Bruh
description: Aki and Suna take a rehabilitated Ice Man out for a day in the city, but things take a turn for the worse as he misinterprets their cues and turns a game of hover hockey into a literal freeze out!

title: Hide and Seek
description: A game of hide and seek uncovers a neglected remnant from Uncle Grandpa's past.

title: Curses/Bang for Your Buck
description: Curses: When Bubbles overhears the Professor saying some bad words, the girls add a whole new slew of adjectives to their vocabulary./Bang for Your Buck: When the girls and the Gangreen Gang discover a destructo ray for sale at Mojo's Yard Sale, each team sets out to see who can earn the most money and buy it first.

title: Best Day Ever
description: Joker frees Luthor with a mother box and forces him to spend the day together, hopping all over the world, with the Justice League hot on their trail trying to catch up.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: Alpha Dome
description: The guys confront some people.

title: Boss For a Day
description: When Chata lets Vic be the boss of the taco stand for the day Vic decides to fire Val, which has disastrous consequences.

title: King of the Machines
description: Panthro gets insecure when he finds out Barbastella has a history of dating royalty, so he tries to impress her by becoming "King of the Machines" and giving all the appliances in the Cats' Lair artificial intelligence.

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Vengeance Is Mine!
description: Aspheera arrives at the Monastery of Spinjitzu and confronts Wu, forcing one of the ninja to make a heroic sacrifice.

title: El Club de Exploradores
description: El ninja debe entrar en el Club del Explorador para obtener el segundo Pergamino de Spinjitzu Prohibido, en conflicto con el gerente del club y los miembros furiosos del club.

title: Get Back Jojo
description: Mojo goes back in time to try and stop the Professor from having the inspiration for the perfect little girls. Little does he know that in doing so he provides just the spark the young Professor needs.

title: Best Best Friends
description: Master Frown and Brock attend a friendship-themed competition intending to ruin it for everyone else, but soon discover their own friendship in need of repair.

title: Card Wars
description: Finn and Jake embark on an epic game of Card Quest.

title: Access Denied
description: When Axel and the team try to figure out what Sarge Charge's secret weapon is, they get ejected from the house by his newly upgraded security system and must fight their way back inside before Madcap does.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Your Mother and Mine
description: Steven takes Garnet to meet some of his new friends.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Jelly Aches
description: The school descends into chaos after getting a visit from Gazunga, the Jealousy Troll.

title: Burning Low
description: Finn starts spending a lot of time with Flame Princess. Is Princess Bubblegum jealous?

title: Shun and Lightning/Premonition of a Storm
description: Shun and Lightning: Shun and Lightning are on the hunt for a rare Tumpee, when they run into McQ! With all the devices related crimes happening in Los Volmos, Shun decides to investigate to try to get to the bottom of McQ's nefarious dealings./Premonition of a Storm: After a run in with McQ, Shun and Lightning find themselves in a little bit trouble. They're trapped!  Tied up with no Bakugan to help them escape, and no one knows their whereabouts. It will take some big help to help them get out of this mess.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Escaramuza
description: When Val's favorite Escaramuza team loses a member, he convinces Xochi to join the squad. He becomes her coach and will do anything to win the big competition.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Companera Nueva
description: Zoe construye su propio traje de batalla con la esperanza de unirse al equipo de Axel. ¿El único problema? Ella no puede encogerse! Se producen hijinks cuando una Zoe de tamaño completo intenta ayudar a Axel & co. en una batalla contra Pyrant y su ejército de drones de control mental.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Justice League Edition Part 2
description: In order to be the most talented superhero team in the DC universe, Robin and Beast Boy must work together on a jazz performance.

title: Grounded
description: Uncle Grandpa must fix his mistake after he helps a grounded teen go to a party.

title: Boo-ray for Bizarro
description: When the diabolical Amazo attacks the League and begins to steal their powers one-by-one, the klutzy, backwards-thinking Bizarro becomes our heroes' last hope to turn things around.

title: The Cave of Gelatinous Doom!
description: The Warriors don't have a worthy adventure to use their impressive new skull-and-crossbones-emblazoned Bonehead Magisword until they are sent on a quest to battle a mighty slime beast in the Dungeon of Gelatinous Doom!

title: Lonely Kid
description: When AD has trouble making friends at school, MM tells her the story of how he made his first real friend —BB.

title: A Glitch Is a Glitch
description: Ice King creates a computer virus to delete everybody except him and Princess Bubblegum.

title: Minus Mini
description: When Mega Mini is kidnapped by Blasto Woman, Mega Man must track down his missing partner without the full use of his own systems.

title: Clarence Gets a Girlfriend
description: When Clarence is asked out on a date by Ashley, a girl in his class, he realizes he doesn't know the first thing about having a girlfriend! Clarence enlists Sumo and Jeff to transform himself into the perfect gentleman just in time for his big date.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ninos vergonzosos
description: Owen teme perder a su mejor amigo Noah que se va a una escuela militar.

title: Reunited
description: Steven brings everyone together for a special reunion.

title: Azulejo
description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

title: Fallen Arches/The Mane Event
description: Fallen Arches: When a gang of old-time villains come out of retirement, the girls enlist the best superhero team of the past to save the city./The Mane Event: Bubbles and Buttercup are playing with Blossom's beautiful locks when an accident happens. Now, Blossom is too embarrassed to put up a good fight.

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 2
description: The Autobots distract the Decepticons with an all-out assault on the Threshold of the Well while Bee, Hot Rod, and Cheetor split off for the real mission…

title: Charlie
description: You know that one annoying friend who just can't get the hint? That's Charlie, and he's Bigfoot. The Bears meet him when Charlie signs up on a home-sharing website to spend a weekend with the Bears. Charlie is the worst possible house guest for the Bears and nearly destroys their house.

title: Jessica Goes to the Creek
description: When Craig and Jessica are locked out of the house, Craig has no choice but to bring his little sister to the Creek.

title: Frenemy
description: When the coolest girl in school befriends the girls, she charms them into becoming her accomplices in a series of adventurous crimes.

title: No sin mis choco-lletas
description: Noah intenta rescatar los chocolates que Owen olvidó afuera.

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: Inglorious Toddlers
description: Owen fears he's about to lose his BFF Noah to a gifted military school.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Justice League Edition Part 1
description: The Justice League holds yet another talent competition, only this time they're facing off against the Titans.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Battle for Cybertron II Part 1
description: Megatron's jubilation at destroying the Ark is short-lived as he realizes the ship was a decoy — the Autobots have landed on Cybertron.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val le guarda rencor a Vic, lo cual atrae sin querer a un malvado cadejo, una bestia mitológica parecida a un lobo.

title: Bedside Manners
description: After a nasty spill lands Belson in a full body cast, Clarence pays his bedridden friend a visit at the hospital, but what Clarence thinks will cheer him up might actually drive Belson totally crazy!

title: Simply Perfect
description: When the kids are about to be subject to school testing with no time to study, Courtney freaks and orders a Brainiac Ray from the back of a comic book that does not work as advertised.

title: Jean Jacket
description: The Bears find a bedazzled jean jacket in a dumpster. It's just about the coolest thing they've ever seen and seems to make the wearer of the jacket extremely lucky. But after the Bears fight over who gets control of the jacket, they have to consider that their denim blessing has become a curse.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Second Stage Begins/Mechanoids Attack!
description: The Second Stage Begins: With half of the brawlers eliminated, the second stage of the Bakugan Battle league begins. This round will be a timed race to the finish, with all kinds of tricks and traps that will slow down even the best brawlers./Mechanoids Attack!: Mechanoids have crashed the second stage of the Bakugan Battle League, causing all kinds of havoc. The Awesome Brawlers will now have to race against the clock, battling competitors and mechanoids if they want to make it through this round.

title: Hachiman
description: While on a super important mission to get batteries for the TV remote Lion-O meets Hachiman, a cool Samurai warrior. Now Lion-O will do anything to prove he's just as cool as Hachiman, even if it means risking his own life!

title: Daddy Issues
description: C.J. wants to win a "cut the Cheeser's" card at a mini-golf tournament.

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: Snow Country for Old Men
description: In an attempt to win the holidays, Chef brings snowmen to life to entertain the kids. But when they turn out to be evil, Chef and the kids have to jingle some bells.

title: Glory Days
description: KO does a school report on Carol.

title: The Music Store Thief
description: Apple and Onion have to defend the music store from instrument theft to get a key to the store.

title: Mindful Education
description: Steven and Connie need to learn greater focus to take their training to the next level.

title: Election Day
description: Apple runs for Mayor.

title: Atrapagritos
description: Cuando una caries obliga a Ben a ir al dentista, su día empeora aún más cuando el malévolo mago Hex usa un atrapasueños para materializar los miedos de nuestro héroe y los transporta con él a un lugar pesadillesco.

title: Battle for Cybertron I Part 2
description: Chromia and Perceptor race to warn the Autobots that the Decepticons are waiting for them on Cybertron.

title: Dog Day
description: When a father refuses his daughter's request for a dog, Uncle Grandpa vows to teach the girl responsibility by becoming a dog.

title: Squideo Games
description: When Vambre and Prohyas are hired for separate gigs, they end up having to battle each other to claim a rare Squideo from Lake Sprite in Galacton.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Under Siege
description: Having learned Master Wu is the "Treacherous One," the ninja find themselves under siege at the Monastery, trying to protect Wu from the wrath of Aspheera.

title: Dream Scheme/You Snooze, You Lose
description: Dream Scheme: The Sandman would like a little rest so he puts the world to sleep. The girls must battle him in his dreams to get things back to normal./You Snooze, You Lose: When the Amoeba Boys find Mojo's plan to destroy the Powerpuff Girls, the girls unwittingly help them build a machine for their own destruction.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Face Your Fears
description: Our heroes play an arcade game that makes them face their greatest fears.

title: #FantasticBeastsAndHowToMindThem
description: Diana Prince receives a care package from home, and her pet-raising skills are soon put to the test when a mysterious egg hatches into a baby griffin.

title: La mascara del engano
description: Cuando un sindicato de criminals desconocido amenaza a la Familia Real, los ninjas son llamados de nuevo a la acción y deben proteger a la princesa real y un artefacto legendario que puede tener poderes sobrenaturales.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Bon Voyage
description: Aboard the SS Pettigrew on its final voyage, Ben must not only battle seasickness but Steam Smythe, who looks to use his mechanical creatures to sink the steamship's modern replacement and the passengers with it!

title: Big Bad Dreams
description: When Namagem starts using his Hypno powers to haunt Aki's dreams, our hero must face his fears in the dreamscape.

title: Booster's Gold
description: Green Arrow becomes involved with Booster Gold when he discovers that the self-centered superhero has brought dinosaurs back from the past for a money-making venture.

title: Guidance
description: Amethyst has been helping Little Homeschool Gems find jobs on the boardwalk, but Steven isn't sure about her approach.

title: Christmas Spirit
description: Apple & Onion have to become mall Santas to get the gifts they want for Christmas.

title: Occupy Bears
description: When the city plans to destroy the Bears' cave in order to make way for a new cell phone tower, Grizz and Panda must find evidence from their past that proves they have rights to their land. And in case that fails, Ice Bear protests and tries to sabotage the construction crew.

title: Rock Porcupunk
description: Madcap recurre a Axel y su equipo en busca de ayuda después de que una actualización sónica a Porcupunk amenaza con derribar la casa.

title: Rad
description: With Plumber agents trapped in Incursean territory, Ben and Rook must employ the services of Rad Dudesman, the roughest, toughest smuggler in the galaxy.  (Introducing Rad Dudesman, return of classic Ben alien, Eye Guy.)

title: Never Trust a Human
description: A flashback episode tells the story of Young Wu and Young Garmadon meeting Aspheera and teaching her the secrets of Spinjitzu.

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Cat Videos
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to get Benson to stop watching cat videos.

title: Los Pajaros
description: When Valentino trades Huitzi's gifts for one of his own, the birds in town start to turn on him.

title: Corporate Buyout
description: The Cheetara Corp employee retreat gets canceled when Baron Karnon, a mysterious corporate raider, buys them out! Now Cheetara and Jan-Jan must brave the wilds of Third Earth's most dangerous jungles to find the Baron's office and demand a meeting with the man who stole their company!

title: Acceso Denegado
description: Cuando Axel y el equipo intentan descubrir cuál es el arma secreta de Sarge Charge, son expulsados ​​de la casa por su sistema de seguridad recientemente actualizado y deben abrirse camino antes de que Madcap lo haga.

title: Battle for Cybertron III Part 1
description: While the battle rages on the surface, deep below ground Hot Rod faces off against an unexpected traitor, giving Cheetor and Bee time to get the Allspark to the Well.

title: How to Build a Dragon
description: While Lloyd and the rebels celebrate their successful strike against Emperor Garmadon, in the Realm of Oni and Dragon, the Ninja dare an elaborate escape from the clutches of Iron Baron and his Dragon Hunters.

title: The Debt
description: Gumball resolves to save Mr Robinson's life during Elmore's Senior Talent Show.

title: Keeping It Together
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems revisit the Kindergarten and find a dark secret.

title: Beyond This Earthly Realm
description: When Finn finds a porcelain lamb, it transports him into the spirit world and only the Ice King can help get him out!

title: Film Flam
description: A sleazy director arrives in Townsville to make a film about the Powerpuff Girls. But this Hollywood type wants more out of Townsville than an Oscar-winning film.

title: Adorapapa
description: Cuando el papa de Adorabat le prohíbe trabajar en el departamento del sheriff porque es muy peligroso, Adorabat decide demostrarle que puede cuidarse sola.

title: Screamcatcher
description: When a cavity forces Ben to the dentist his day gets even worse when the malevolent magician Hex uses a nearby dream catcher to bring our hero's fears to life and transports them both to a nightmarish dreamscape.

title: Jefe por un dia
description: Cuando Chata deja que Vic sea el jefe del puesto de tacos por un día, él decide despedir a Val, lo que trae consecuencias desastrosas.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Me, My Elf, and I
description: Duncan tricks Chef into taking the class to the North Pole in order to remove his name from the naughty list.

title: Little Homeschool
description: Welcome to Little Homeschool, a place on earth where Gems from all over the universe can come learn how to live together peacefully! But there's one Gem who refuses to attend.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Birthday Gift
description: Rigby always gives Mordecai the worst birthday gifts, but this year it's going to be different.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Club
description: When Gumball rejects "The Rejects Club", the rejects wreak their revenge.

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Showdown Part I
description: The Faction infiltrates Galvan in an attempt to destroy Azmuth.  (Introducing new Nemetrix aliens Omnivoracious & Vicetopus.)

title: The Answer
description: Garnet finally tells Steven the story of how she came to be a Crystal Gem.

title: The Hex Factor
description: When Hex mistakes an exclusive magic club for a top-secret Wizard society that snubbed him, Ben has to figure out how to work around the club's strict code of conduct to stop him without getting booted by security.

title: The Date
description: Gumball discovers the difference between a "date" and a "pet's funeral"...the hard way.

title: El Ladron de Musica
description: Manzana y Cebollín tienen que defender la tienda de música del robo de instrumentos para conseguir una llave de la tienda.

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: They Lurk Below
description: Max's old friend has built the world's only underwater resort, and Ben, Gwen and Max are invited for a sneak peak. But it turns out in order to power the resort, Max's friend took an energy orb from a race of underwater aliens. Now, the aliens want their energy orb back and destroy the resort in order to get it.

title: Chili Cook-Off
description: Benson wants to get some street cred with the Park Managers' Association and win the big chili cook-off.

title: The Other Side: The Tournament
description: The Tournament - Hoping to win a special prize for his Dad's birthday, Craig and his friends compete in a tournament on the Other Side of the Creek!

title: Hierro y piedra
description: Cole y Wu Joven intentan liberar a sus amigos, que han sido capturados por una tribu de Cazadores de Dragones. Mientras tanto en Ninjago, Lloyd se reúne con unos viejos amigos que quizás sean aliados valiosos contra el Emperador Garmadon.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: A Cold Goodbye
description: Having learned Zane is not dead, Master Wu prepares to go after him, but Lloyd and the other ninja take matters into their own hands and defy their Master.

title: Average Jeff
description: Jeff suffers an identity crisis when a standardized test lands him in the lesser of the classes academic groupings.

title: Pumm-Ra
description: Mumm-Ra plans to disguise himself as a Thunderian and infiltrate Cats' Lair, but the Ancient Spirits of Evil are mad at him and won't give him any magic today. No matter, Mumm-Ra knows what a ThunderCat looks like so he slaps on some awful, unconvincing, cat make up and heads to Cats' Lair to introduce himself!

title: The Frogs of War Part 2
description: With Ben missing, the Incurseans now control the Earth. It's up to Rook and the remaining Plumbers to lead the resistance and fight back! (Introducing new Ben alien, Bullfrag.)

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Dream of Love
description: Tree Trunks is courted by an oinking suitor, but much to Jake's dismay, this interferes with her baking habits.

title: The Fog
description: A new villain arrives in Townsville and gives the old villains an enticing offer.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Sitiados
description: Habiendo aprendido que el Maestro Wu es el "Traicionero", los ninja se encuentran asediados en el Monasterio, tratando de proteger a Wu de la ira de Aspheera.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Una Fria Despedida
description: Habiendo aprendido que Zane no está muerto, el Maestro Wu se prepara para ir tras él, pero Lloyd y el otro ninja toman el asunto en sus propias manos y desafían a su Maestro.

title: #TweenTitans
description: Jessica Cruz is hired by billionaire playboy Bruce Wayne to chaperone young Dick Grayson's Metropolis birthday bash and brings Karen Beecher along to help, but the girls get more than they bargained for when the TWEEN party guests reveal their TITANic personalities.

title: More of the Same
description: Can the Titans master the four New Year's traditions in order to break the cycle of bad years?

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: The Unikingdom Awards
description: Unikitty throws an elaborate award show for everyone in the Unikingdom, including Master Frown and Brock, but tensions rise when Frown fails to win an award.

title: Como construir un dragon
description: Mientras Lloyd y los rebeldes celebran su exitoso golpe contra el Emperador Garmadon, en el Reino de Oni y Dragón, los Ninjas se aventuran con un elaborado escape de las garras del Barón de Hierro y sus Cazadores de Dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Journey to Maize Mountain Part 2
description: When Victor and Valentino destroy Monte Macabre's corn supply, they journey to Maíz Mountain with Sal to replace it. But in order to get the corn, they must shrink down to the size of ants and embark on a mythical adventure that they'll never forget!

title: Driver's Test
description: When a girl has trouble passing her driving test, Uncle Grandpa shows up to help her.  But when they accidentally set a Crazy Baby loose in the city, it's up to Uncle Grandpa to stop it... by teaching the girl how to drive!

title: Adoradad
description: When AD's dad forbids her from working with the Sheriff's Dept because it's too dangerous, AD sets out to prove that she can take care of herself.

title: You're Everybody's Sidekick
description: KO sets out to prove to Enid that being helpful is rewarding by helping people all around the Lakewood Plaza Turbo.

title: The Mask of Deception
description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

title: Christmas Crusaders
description: Santa Claus and Robin must stop the nefarious Coal Miner.

title: Berb-cules
description: The ThunderCats finally sit the Berbils down and tell them they really shouldn't be building things for the Mutants anymore, it's time for the Berbils to stand up for themselves. The Berbils take this advice way too far and build a giant, building-sized, Berbil named Berbcules. Berb-cules takes back everything the Berbils ever built for the Mutants and everything they ever built for the ThunderCats! Now Panthro has to figure out a way to a defeat the most powerful invention the best little builders have ever built!

title: Chalmers Santiago
description: While Clarence spends a lazy Saturday playing 8-bit adventure game Dragon's Cusp, Mary asks him to return some mail to the guy across the street Chalmers Santiago, whom they've never seen. Clarence makes it his mission to befriend the mysterious neighbor, only to find out it's someone he knows quite well.

title: Conoce a Tu Mama
description: K.O. quiere sorprender a Carol con un regalo para el Día de la Madre, pero no sabe qué comprarle.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Los Perdidos
description: When Vic joins a group of nighttime skaters called Los Perdidos, Val becomes suspicious of Vic's strange, new, vampire-like behavior.

title: Primogenita
description: El Emperador Garmadon ha tomado el control de Ciudad Ninjago donde Lloyd se retira hacia las sombras. Mientras tanto, los otros Ninjas y Wu Joven quedan varados en el Reino de Oni y Dragón y descubren que no están solos.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Jessica va al Arroyo
description: Cuando Craig y Jessica quedan encerrados fuera de la casa, Craig no tiene otra opción: debe llevar a su hermanita al Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Beast Boy on a Shelf
description: Santa Claus forces Beast Boy to become a spy and report on the Titans' naughty behavior.

title: All Aboard the Space Train
description: In a strange turn of events, the JLA enlist the help of Space Cabbie and Jonah Hex to stop the hijacking of an intergalactic space train.

title: The Car
description: Gumball and Darwin accidentally destroy Mr Robinson's new car...or do they?

title: Blue Ribbon Blues
description: When a famous scientist comes to the school, Blossom will stop at nothing to impress him at the Science Fair even if that means putting Townsville in danger!

title: Shush Ninjas
description: The Bears are fed up with the decay of etiquette at today's theaters. The Bears take it upon themselves to be the police of the theater, sneaking up like ninjas to shush people who ruin the movie for others with their bad manners.

title: Radio Free NinjaGo
description: Lloyd must find his voice as he leads a small resistance to capture the airwaves in Ninjago City. Meanwhile in the First Realm, Iron Baron takes the Ninja on a dragon hunt.

title: Dinner Party
description: When Clarence's mom takes Clarence to a stuffy dinner party, Clarence embarks on a quest for fun wherever it can be found.

title: Midnight Madness
description: When the Rustbucket breaks down outside the largest mall in the U.S., it seems Ben and Gwen will have the time of their lives in the mall. That is until they run into an evil hypnotist entertaining the crowd, who puts Ben under hypnosis, causing him to sleepwalk at night and help him steal things. And when the hypnotist discovers certain aliens are now helping him, he exploits them for his grand plan of hypnotizing hundreds of people so they'll be under his demented control forever. Ben must figure out how to break the spell he's under and stop this evil plan.

title: Apple & Onion's Booth
description: Apple and Onion must save their favorite booth at Pizza's Diner from a Texas oil tycoon.

title: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition/Battle Royal
description: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition: It's the start of the Bakugan Battle League - Toyko edition! The first round will be a Battle Royale style competition, where only half the competitors will make it through to the next round. Along with the Awesome brawlers the field of competitors is filled with familiar friends and foes./Battle Royal: The first round of the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo edition continues. The Awesome Brawler's and their Bakugan battle their way through the challenge and face off against tough competitors.

title: Mao Mao's Nakey
description: When MM loses his clothes while trying to scale the Ruby Pure Heart, he has to get back to Sheriff's HQ by daybreak.

title: A Guilded Cage
description: Mega Man must stop Namagem and an army of hypnotized Good Guild bots from breaking into Dr. Light's lab.

title: Battle for Cybertron III Part 2
description: Windblade, Wheeljack, and Teletraan-X make a play for Vector Sigma.

title: Dias de gloria
description: K.O. escribe un informe escolar sobre Carol.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Trick or Creek
description: It's Halloween at the Creek, and Craig is on a mission to collect as much candy as humanly possible, but a spooky ghoul from the Creek's past threatens his haul.

title: Journey to Maize Mountain Part 1
description: When Vic & Val destroy Monte Macabre's corn supply, they travel with Sal to Corn Mountain to replace it. But in order to get the corn, they have to shrink to the size of ants, creating all kinds of problems!

title: La Taza del Patito de la Suerte
description: Cuando Adorabat y Colosal rompen la taza favorita de Mao Mao, el sheriff los castiga con su silencio.

title: The Oni & the Dragon
description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

title: Consejos
description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

title: Charlie
description: ¿Viste cuando tienes un amigo que no entiende una indirecta? Ese es Charlie, Pie Grande. Los Osos lo conocen cuando Charlie se inscribe en un sitio web para personas que comparten su casa y se instala un fin de semana con los Osos. Charlie es el peor invitado posible para los Osos y prácticamente destruye la casa.

title: Tagalong
description: Buttercup is tired of Bubbles following her everywhere.

title: Know Your Mom
description: KO wants to surprise Carol with a gift for Mother's Day, but doesn't know what to get her.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Baby Mouth
description: In order to find out about his family history, Robin takes a DNA test and discovers he's from Babylon.

title: Iron & Stone
description: Cole and Young Wu attempt to free their friends, who have been taken captive by a tribe of Dragon Hunters. Meanwhile in Ninjago, Lloyd is reunited with some old friends who may prove valuable allies against Emperor Garmadon.

title: The Very Best Candy
description: The gang can't decide which of their candy is the best, so they turn it sentient and have it fight to determine the winner.

title: Enfrenta Tus Miedos
description: Nuestros héroes juegan un juego de un tragamonedas que los hace enfrentarse a sus temores más grandes.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: El oni y el dragon
description: Mientras que la Princesa Harumi se adapta a la vida con los ninjas, Lloyd y Jay buscan respuestas sobre las máscaras Oni, mientras que Cole y Zane intentan infiltrarse en Los Hijos de Garmadon.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol
